0.6.name: wordpress/ultimate-category-excluder
0.6.description: Ultimate Category Excluder (UCE - unfortunately the same abbreviation as unsolicited commercial email) is a WordPress plugin that allows you to quickly and easily exclude categories from your front page, archives, and feeds. Just select which categories you want to be excluded, and UCE does all the work for you!
